</div><!-- end hu -->

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ ENGLISH ═══ -->
<div data-lang="en">
<h2 id="enchanting-overview">✨ Enchanting</h2>
<p>MITE: Break Everything features three enchanting tables. The basic one gives random enchantments, while the most advanced (Custom) lets you <strong>choose specific enchantments</strong> for XP — no bookshelves needed.</p>

<h2 id="enchanting-tables">Enchanting Tables Comparison</h2>
